Description: Light weight and spacious casual backpack with 2 compartments and 1 front easy-access pocket. The front and back of the backpack are fully padded for cushioning. It has organiser for pens, visiting cards, etc along with space for carrying papers, files, books, etc. It is spacious enough to keep all your stuff. It has provision for holding bottles/unmrella on both sides and has adjustable padded shoulder straps for your comfort. The logo of the bag is Reflective so it will glow when light hits it which is a very important safety feature, specially when on road.

Description: When looking for the best home gym equipment and workout essentials, Aurion has you covered. Our brand provides a variety of quality products ranging from weightlifting belts to boxing gloves and more. At Aurion, we understand that physical activity plays a crucial role in maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Our durable and reliable gym equipment provides you with an effective workout anywhere and at any time of the day. Our products are designed to meet any budget and are made for rough and extended use. Whether toning up your biceps or refining your abs, we ensure you have the perfect training setup for any kind of exercise while still being lightweight and space-saving. Aurion is your partner in achieving your health and fitness goals! We provide everything you need to stay in shape – dumbbells, skipping ropes, punching bags, fitness kits, weightlifting belts, and much more! Our carefully selected equipment features premium materials that ensure maximum durability and reliability. Aurion is committed to providing top-quality products. We also house an extensive range of sports equipment like bags, volleyballs, footballs, and cricket bats. So, no matter what sport or activity you’re passionate about, Aurion has the right gear for you. With our reliable products and budget-friendly prices – we’re ready to become a part of your fitness story!

Description: Vault backpack is the only true ant theft backpack in the market. With an anti theft construction which keeps your laptop close to you, It also has an actual fixed lock so your belongings are always Completely secure. To protect your credit and debit cards, there is a dedicated rid pocket for your wallet. It also comes with a USB port to charge your devices on the go. The main compartment has been thoughtfully designed with tiny pockets so you can keep all your stuff organized.
